itunes:summary:
In this special episode, Rocco calls Ross to talk about the recent hard times he's been going through. Hopefully, this episode encourages you to call a friend if you're feeling low. A Drinkin' Bro will be there for you. Forgive the quality, it was a spur of the moment phone call. Stay tuned after the show for a special airing of one Rocco's motivational speeches.
